{"type":"message","id":"e3927d7a","parentId":"6094d7b3","timestamp":"2026-04-17T04:01:15.906Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Yes, let’s define the contract.\n\nHere’s a clean starting structure we can fill in together:\n\n1. Purpose and scope\n2. Parties involved\n3. Deliverables\n4. Timeline and milestones\n5. Roles and responsibilities\n6. Payment / consideration\n7. Acceptance criteria\n8. Change process\n9. Confidentiality\n10. Termination\n11. Dispute / governing terms\n12. Sign-off\n\nIf you want, I can draft a first-pass contract now.\n\nJust send me either:\n- the actual deal terms, or\n- even rough notes/bullets\n\nand I’ll turn them into contract language.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_02ad8e5e7b4217730169e1b0899f8c8191b3bbb455b75a6984\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":835,"output":134,"cacheRead":7040,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":8009,"cost":{"input":0.0020875000000000004,"output":0.00201,"cacheRead":0.0017599999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0058575}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776398471912,"responseId":"resp_02ad8e5e7b4217730169e1b08836f48191b6673375a18d4f40"}}
