{"type":"message","id":"149f88f1","parentId":"cd7498c6","timestamp":"2026-04-17T04:12:28.412Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Searching for memory files**\n\nI see that the old memory file is just a test entry, so it’s not really useful. I think I should explore the legacy workspace more thoroughly, particularly checking if there's a memory folder or a MEMORY.md file. I’m curious whether the naming convention, like using lowercase, could be affecting my search too. So my next step is to search through the files under legacy/Intel/workspace to find what I'm looking for.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_02ad8e5e7b4217730169e1b3285e0c81919a8ba0e00d5f39c0\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp4bMrAHRS0ssDvGmaOGxZvnhemQoeujnfVajvYonmU1MYq0xEyCtcOBIHnpI8QHd5dLoMXE0w7fjtSsre6WAlcArUZWQa3uI8poqZDPw0vm2nvitv6ViWAy0FBjd2M0CkajDOI-bUJiQmgUc10iBXxVzblG6z8tJYRt8mmu6nwaX7v43h6LvnPu7d33nUtMVrR3GKgx52Q6aSSc-w_WXE9828l1idiz8I8O7LzpgwE-dtHDWP27qMlancXWK7TjZ7kNlOS5U5emoykQZq7Q9ed4zzxApe1l1hfiG9zsuwDsWpYNHkPipM6GkRG-6WjQrS91T9O8QhvpLnh-MMe2MhbygzfdSB88Pp7f6yjFfq8QQMgzv6Ab72BNzfk3iwUwrZlTlEUsGbdBGXS_5eML5RS_7VEOAWVnhMAANLoxGSkIyQp8gbfcaDJMKKU7f24nkud5kuoQ6bYPfvptyw3LTF5d1VXNLpwo1xOzAidOa27xTx-WMFp_vz02Mn78c3217RLwfK7InzZeDQqN-H19c6jxZtZrD9_WaQYIfFEZs2RWni0IEfaWrUOZ88PorN2gkjSJMx-rBpem8__BqvShDG17xzut0sil3EK6HPF5UZF4nZeZhN65Tq1Fz4y6pjSpsCytqPjFRZs3bXPgarAOEJQeNroOHHhW0F-dnz36o5v6SC9HC2ICI1-wTNSDmnaxZ7JMNhouqnmPOpCcS6Mt9phCO9jJChO81gfrTAkdssCmdUyhOclWUI0fwtdi-EHyxSESE2fCJcxpjJ8Vf5g38_Ikq8X4iqmvqJuAUY3Bfv8EDnTacE34aB5UaY3SOHVYCbPj3MwYGnkIITw0W2mVbQG0Sr5i8bAAMkZO-Wdr6ytPkjrrbAKNL8T8-5j3bEDhcNcCpF2p2fQjDjB7O-6HKf0ZkZQYwE2XpKTn2usrSoYwfs70Oq9V2oKxJKCIOFpsvr8SeGu8MSbqqOfvUUQFR6LV2bo_auL-G9awZAJcgOF8dEbkuqfmZV0C_D_-E08j1xlknY74J1EAni_5Y2IqX5iPgmvg6ARKrA-VCeVX8wbgh9LvuwCW7uL8R7xEfOs4mL4nNOtHSUVi5wiJIRcBnhKYXe-fkhLHHSpdCUhfx9tjQOQpnwv_-GPibTOA9Vgpg27N0aY6si4kiw0EAdUpjuajCJy96nIdnbdPxM7VFBT55Si-kPS3uEowr7T29TdkglQg61NYbXxCXwWWEV6RvRoeufSQ==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Searching for memory files**\\n\\nI see that the old memory file is just a test entry, so it’s not really useful. I think I should explore the legacy workspace more thoroughly, particularly checking if there's a memory folder or a MEMORY.md file. I’m curious whether the naming convention, like using lowercase, could be affecting my search too. So my next step is to search through the files under legacy/Intel/workspace to find what I'm looking for.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"The `Intel/memory.md` copy is basically empty, just a test line. I’m checking the legacy workspace next in case the real old memory lived there instead.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_02ad8e5e7b4217730169e1b32b5a588191aea9c737b0d432ff\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_h4yECLH0hkDNasFKqcdltrp6|fc_02ad8e5e7b4217730169e1b32c846881918070de7abcc2bb7f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find legacy/Intel/workspace -maxdepth 4 \\( -iname '*memory*' -o -iname 'MEMORY.md' -o -iname 'memory.md' \\) | sort","workdir":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace","yieldMs":10000},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"find legacy/Intel/workspace -maxdepth 4 \\\\( -iname '*memory*' -o -iname 'MEMORY.md' -o -iname 'memory.md' \\\\) | sort\",\"workdir\":\"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace\",\"yieldMs\":10000}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2mIHuWWIanrSl5347fLBO0Gc|fc_02ad8e5e7b4217730169e1b32c84848191a44dd54dc2151ed1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"legacy/Intel/workspace/BOOTSTRAP.md"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"legacy/Intel/workspace/BOOTSTRAP.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_tmS3RF5PvDTR7orWG9Qf7XEx|fc_02ad8e5e7b4217730169e1b32c848c8191914b508e68af0e21","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"legacy/archive-report-2026-04-16.md"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"legacy/archive-report-2026-04-16.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":773,"output":228,"cacheRead":15872,"cach