{"type":"message","id":"71d02997","parentId":"1756440a","timestamp":"2026-04-17T04:13:38.238Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_KXUp4Ik9Sm4VQBu4TJJI2nvu|fc_02ad8e5e7b4217730169e1b36e73688191a98626a9e58ed22f","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"memory/2026-04-17.md","content":"# 2026-04-17\n\n- The root `MEMORY.md` was discovered missing after the session history was lost when the PC went into standby.\n- Searched for old memory copies. `Intel/memory.md` exists but only contained a test line, so it was not useful as a real recovery source.\n- Recovered Apollo continuity from `projects/apollo/` control docs and from the archived session note `legacy/Intel/workspace/memory/2026-04-16-lightrag-ingestion.md`.\n- Rebuilt a fresh root `MEMORY.md` with the durable Apollo context and continuity rules.\n- Added a `memory/backups/` backup path and a simple backup script so future `MEMORY.md` changes can be mirrored.\n- Updated `AGENTS.md` with instructions to restore `MEMORY.md` from backup if it ever goes missing again.\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"memory/2026-04-17.md\",\"content\":\"# 2026-04-17\\n\\n- The root `MEMORY.md` was discovered missing after the session history was lost when the PC went into standby.\\n- Searched for old memory copies. `Intel/memory.md` exists but only contained a test line, so it was not useful as a real recovery source.\\n- Recovered Apollo continuity from `projects/apollo/` control docs and from the archived session note `legacy/Intel/workspace/memory/2026-04-16-lightrag-ingestion.md`.\\n- Rebuilt a fresh root `MEMORY.md` with the durable Apollo context and continuity rules.\\n- Added a `memory/backups/` backup path and a simple backup script so future `MEMORY.md` changes can be mirrored.\\n- Updated `AGENTS.md` with instructions to restore `MEMORY.md` from backup if it ever goes missing again.\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":217,"output":217,"cacheRead":26752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27186,"cost":{"input":0.0005425,"output":0.003255,"cacheRead":0.0066879999999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0104855}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776399213333,"responseId":"resp_02ad8e5e7b4217730169e1b36da4188191ac8ebf3ddf5b7f35"}}
