 environment audit! I also need to look at the restart policies in the compose file and check if the service data mount directories and volumes exist. \\n\\nUsing `find` on the data directory could be useful, though there might be permission issues with the data/postgres. I think I can still list the root directory. It might be good to create structured audit categories like strong, fragile, and urgent, and mention things like restarts and backup daemons. So, let's proceed with the update_plan and do some reads and execs.\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9y9lvbCTELrwRH6Qf0Zl9zmK|fc_02ad8e5e7b4217730169e1b9dfa0408191b933c5643397e334","name":"update_plan","arguments":{"plan":[{"step":"Inspect environment files, runtime layout, and Apollo control docs for audit signals","status":"in_progress"},{"step":"Assess what looks solid versus fragile in the current Apollo workspace/environment","status":"pending"},{"step":"Summarize the audit with risks, strengths, and immediate recommendations","status":"pending"}]},"partialJson":"{\"plan\":[{\"step\":\"Inspect environment files, runtime layout, and Apollo control docs for audit signals\",\"status\":\"in_progress\"},{\"step\":\"Assess what looks solid versus fragile in the current Apollo workspace/environment\",\"status\":\"pending\"},{\"step\":\"Summarize the audit with risks, strengths, and immediate recommendations\",\"status\":\"pending\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":9381,"output":592,"cacheRead":50688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60661,"cost":{"input":0.0234525,"output":0.00888,"cacheRead":0.012672,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0450045}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776400843815,"responseId":"resp_02ad8e5e7b4217730169e1b9cc8b8481918d76eae8bff096a4"}}
