{"type":"message","id":"f384cd3d","parentId":"09b40f4a","timestamp":"2026-04-17T04:45:53.523Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Fri 2026-04-17 04:45 UTC] we're getting lost in the weeds with too many words but thank you. \n\nPlease audit docker-compose.yaml and consider hardening: it must survive system standby / restarts. there are also 2 files called apollo_up.bat and apollo_down.bat whose purpose is to automate and integrate startup and shutdown processesn in a comprehensive and elegant way. pleasea udit those as well"}],"timestamp":1776401153518}}
