nputs\\n- what ingestion path we should automate next\\n\\nIf you want, I can start on step 2 right after you provide the compose file.\",\"textSignature\":\"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_0beebb82725bec5a0169e097f7ed808191b7625ea80e1ac136\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"}],\"api\":\"openai-codex-responses\",\"provider\":\"openai-codex\",\"model\":\"gpt-5.4\",\"usage\":{\"input\":179,\"output\":476,\"cacheRead\":53888,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":54543,\"cost\":{\"input\":0.00044750000000000004,\"output\":0.0071400000000000005,\"cacheRead\":0.013472,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0.021059500000000002}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1776326647001,\"responseId\":\"resp_0beebb82725bec5a0169e097f6fb8481919279920b5813a66b\"}}\n\n⚠️ [Content truncated during persistence — original exceeded size limit. Use offset/limit parameters or request specific sections for large content.]"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":106,"aggregated":"===== Intel/agents/main/sessions/5c3a7f85-0d14-4d10-a540-96977da5f241.jsonl =====\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"2caed022\",\"parentId\":\"4f4dd462\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-17T06:20:43.326Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"toolResult\",\"toolCallId\":\"call_8ShcX3GgWyNNm6xqpxWOKIeN|fc_02ad8e5e7b4217730169e1d13afd588191855d1e5167725d5f\",\"toolName\":\"edit\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in memory/2026-04-17.md.\"}],\"details\":{\"diff\":\"    ...\\n  6 - Rebuilt a fresh root `MEMORY.md` with the durable Apollo context and continuity rules.\\n  7 - Added a `memory/backups/` backup path and a simple backup script so future `MEMORY.md` changes can be mirrored.\\n  8 - Updated `AGENTS.md` with instructions to restore `MEMORY.md` from backup if it ever goes missing again.\\n  9 - Added a local `scripts/memory_backup_daemon.sh` watchdog and started it with a 10-minute interval so `MEMORY.md` is backed up automatically.\\n+10 - The user added a new workspace rule: befor