to establish the system itself. i would like to discuss the conceptuals of the system without diluting the technical conversation we have had so far\"}],\"timestamp\":1776346234938}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"b195e1d0\",\"parentId\":\"49df63fb\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-16T13:30:39.005Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"call_2n42oBy2z8RWKQTxC9mclekN|fc_0156872873475ee30169e0e47d1b10819190a6b606a8de804d\",\"name\":\"update_plan\",\"arguments\":{\"explanation\":\"The branch scope is now clear, so I’m spawning a conceptual side session.\",\"plan\":[{\"step\":\"Choose the branch task to delegate\",\"status\":\"completed\"},{\"step\":\"Spawn a side session for that branch\",\"status\":\"in_progress\"},{\"step\":\"Return control instructions and next options\",\"status\":\"pending\"}]},\"partialJson\":\"{\\\"explanation\\\":\\\"The branch scope is now clear, so I’m spawning a conceptual side session.\\\",\\\"plan\\\":[{\\\"step\\\":\\\"Choose the branch task to delegate\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"completed\\\"},{\\\"step\\\":\\\"Spawn a side session for that branch\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"in_progress\\\"},{\\\"step\\\":\\\"Return control instructions and next options\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"pending\\\"}]}\"}],\"api\":\"openai-codex-responses\",\"provider\":\"openai-codex\",\"model\":\"gpt-5.4\",\"usage\":{\"input\":219,\"output\":78,\"cacheRead\":61056,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":61353,\"cost\":{\"input\":0.0005475,\"output\":0.00117,\"cacheRead\":0.015264,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0.0169815}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1776346234955,\"responseId\":\"resp_0156872873475ee30169e0e47bfe048191a2f8e771872fd4e9\"}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"35e79dee\",\"parentId\":\"b195e1d0\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-16T13:30:39.023Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"toolResult\",\"toolCallId\":\"call_2n42oBy2z8RWKQTxC9mclekN|fc_0156872873475ee30169e0e47d1b10819190a6b606a8de804d\",\"toolName\":\"update_plan\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Plan updated.\"}],\"details\":{\"status\":\"updated\",\"explanation\":\"The branch scope is now clear, so I’m spawning a conceptual side session.\",\"plan\":[{\"step\":\"Choose the branch task to delegate\",\"status\":\"completed\"},{\"step\":\"Spawn a side session for that branch\",\"status\":\"in_progress\"},{\"step\":\"Return control instructions and next options\",\"status\":\"pending\"}]},\"isError\":false,\"timestamp\":1776346239021}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"38a9f196\",\"parentId\":\"35e79dee\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-16T13:30:45.417Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I’m spinning up a separate branch for the high-level system-concept discussion so we can keep this thread technical and clean.\",\"textSignature\":\"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_0156872873475ee30169e0e48085148191ba6d5db1d9add584\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"commentary\\\"}\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"call_xo5j2IS6OqtqvJudPMJ3Q0m3|fc_0156872873475ee30169e0e4834b188191b17d39a7611f1143\",\"name\":\"sessions_spawn\",\"arguments\":{\"runtime\":\"subagent\",\"mode\":\"session\",\"thread\":false,\"cleanup\":\"keep\",\"cwd\":\"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace\",\"label\":\"apollo-system-conceptuals\",\"task\":\"You are opening a parallel branch of work for a high-level conceptual analysis of the Apollo system. The user wants to discuss the system itself, not the project corpora it will later operate on. Focus on architecture philosophy, operating model, roles of components, orchestration patterns, boundaries between OpenClaw, LightRAG, Open WebUI, local models, cloud reasoning, ingestion strategy, and how Apollo should evolve from a tool stack into a coherent system. Keep it strategic and conceptual, not bogged down in low-level implementation unless needed to clarify a concept. Begin by briefly framing Apollo as a system and invite the user into that conceptual discussion.\",\"timeoutSeconds\":120},\"partialJson\":\"{\\\"runtime\\\":\\\"subagent\\\",\\\"mode\\\":\\\"session\\\",\\\"thread\\\":false,\\\"cleanup\\\":\\\"keep\\\",\\\"cwd\\\":\\\"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"apollo-system-conceptuals\\\",\\\"task\\\":\\\"You are opening a parallel branch of work for a high-level conceptual analysis of the Apollo system. The user wants to discuss the system itself, not the project corpora it will later operate on. Focus on architecture philosophy, operating model, roles of components, orchestration patterns, boundaries between OpenClaw, LightRAG, Open WebUI, local models, cloud reasoning, ingestion strategy, and how Apollo should evolve from a tool stack into a coherent system. Keep it strategic and conceptual, not bogged down in low-level implementation unless needed to clarify a concept. Begin by briefly framing Apollo as a system and invite the user into that conceptual discussion.\\\",\\\"timeoutSeconds\\\":120}\"}],\"api\":\"openai-codex-responses\",\"provider\":\"openai-codex\",\"model\":\"gpt-5.4\",\"usage\":{\"input\":183,\"output\":221,\"cacheRead\":61184,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":61588,\"cost\":{\"input\":0.00045750000000000006,\"output\":0.0033150000000000002,\"cacheRead\":0.015295999999999999,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0.0190685}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1776346239027,\"responseId\":\"resp_0156872873475ee30169e0e47f7318819192fb98c1ea0deb6e\"}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"721c37ab\",\"parentId\":\"38a9f196\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-16T13:30:45.439Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"toolResult\",\"toolCallId\":\"call_xo5j2IS6OqtqvJudPMJ3Q0m3|fc_0156872873475ee30169e0e4834b188191b17d39a7611f1143\",\"toolName\":\"sessions_spawn\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"{\\n  \\\"status\\\": \\\"error\\\",\\n  \\\"error\\\": \\\"mode=\\\\\\\"session\\\\\\\" requires thread=true so the subagent can stay bound to a thread.\\\"\\n}\"}],\"details\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"error\":\"mode=\\\"session\\\" requires thread=true so the subagent can