Qi4Ty7TTR3_jEzfiGQ--vnF_OI_RVee96qGi2tmKFsG1oWuBUVDSJOnAXVEBv59RjCCod2rqZsLZhVYbCISy2dxpIwE66JJ6gQl5hFtEvBE48gFLBIHwvBJdLlZ_UJDTK91se-ysuEhE=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Summarizing changes and next steps**\\n\\nI need to provide a concise update. I should mention that backups have been created and outline the main changes made. I want to include a caution about n8n not being switched, as well as the fact that validation hasn't been performed due to the lack of a Docker CLI. It might be good to suggest rewriting batch scripts as the next step and to clarify any assumptions regarding the health check command. I'll keep it brief since the user requested fewer words.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"Done.\n\nBackups created first:\n- `legacy/Backups/docker-compose.yaml.v2.2026-04-17T06-51-17Z.bak`\n- `legacy/Backups/.env.v2.2026-04-17T06-51-17Z.bak`\n\nChanged:\n\n- `docker-compose.yaml`\n  - added `restart: unless-stopped` to all services\n  - added `init: true`\n  - added `stop_grace_period`\n  - added healthchecks for core services\n  - changed core secrets to `.env` references\n  - kept remote-exposed ports unchanged\n  - made `apollo-agent`, `lightrag`, and `open-webui` wait for healthy `ollama`\n\n- `.env`\n  - preserved `APOLLO_TOKEN`\n  - added:\n    - `POSTGRES_PASSWORD`\n    - `WEBUI_SECRET_KEY`\n    - `N8N_ENCRYPTION_KEY`\n\nImportant conservative choice:\n- I **did not** switch `n8n` to Postgres, to avoid breaking the existing SQLite-backed state already in `data/n8n/`.\n\nAlso updated Apollo continuity docs:\n- `projects/apollo/status.md`\n- `projects/apollo/checklist.md`\n- `projects/apollo/decisions.md`\n- `projects/apollo/status.json`\n\nOne limitation:\n- I could not validate the compose file against live Docker from here because Docker CLI is not available in this session.\n\nNext best step:\n- rewrite `apollo_up.bat` and `apollo_down.bat` to use readiness/health checks instead of fixed sleeps.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_02ad8e5e7b4217730169e1d93eab0481919f29926dc5451d3d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":15225,"output":396,"cacheRead":120320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":135941,"cost":{"input":0.038062500000000006,"output":0.00594,"cacheRead":0.03008,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.07408250000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776408888237,"responseId":"resp_02ad8e5e7b4217730169e1d9392a5c8191b5e03954a248d839"}}
