2 3. verify what LightRAG is actually reading from `Vault/Clean`\n+63 4. define and/or verify the indexing path for the clean corpus\n+64 5. prove the admin query loop with canonical Apollo questions\n+65 6. keep secrets and irrelevant runtime debris out of the retrieval surface\n 66 \n 67 ## Known issues / open operational concerns\n 68 - Git inside the container currently reports a safe-directory ownership issue\n 69 - Path naming conventions should be kept consistent (`Vault/...` rather than mixed variants in project docs/scripts)\n    ...","firstChangedLine":29},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776409158157}}
