{"type":"message","id":"e51e7b75","parentId":"4ecfd772","timestamp":"2026-04-17T07:09:30.912Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Recovery playbook:\n\n## Run order\n1. `apollo_down.bat`\n2. `apollo_up.bat`\n\n## Expected\n- this chat may disconnect\n- services may take a few minutes to come back\n- temporary failures during startup are most likely healthcheck-related\n\n## First checks if something goes wrong\nRun these on the host in `C:\\Apollo`:\n\n```bat\ndocker compose ps\ndocker compose logs --tail=100 ollama\ndocker compose logs --tail=100 apollo-agent\ndocker compose logs --tail=100 open-webui\ndocker compose logs --tail=100 apollo-lightrag\ndocker compose logs --tail=100 docling\ndocker compose logs --tail=100 n8n\ndocker compose logs --tail=100 n8n_db\n```\n\n## What I’ll want you to paste back\nPaste:\n1. output of `docker compose ps`\n2. logs for any service marked:\n   - `unhealthy`\n   - `exited`\n   - or missing\n\n## Most likely failure modes\n1. healthcheck command missing inside an image\n2. service starts slowly and times out\n3. one service depends on Ollama and waits too long\n4. `apollo-agent` comes up late, so webchat looks dead for a bit\n\n## Fast triage hints\n- if containers are **running** but `apollo_up.bat` failed, suspect healthchecks\n- if `apollo-agent` is down, OpenClaw chat won’t come back\n- if `open-webui` is down, UI on port 3000 won’t come back\n- if `ollama` is down, several others may fail secondarily\n\n## Safety fallback\nIf the new config is bad, you still have backups:\n- `legacy/Backups/docker-compose.yaml.v3...`\n- earlier `v2` and `v1`\n- `.env` backups too\n\nSo worst case, you can restore the prior files and bring the stack back up again.\n\nGood moment to proceed.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_02ad8e5e7b4217730169e1dca339ec8191a84a087bc91b0c88\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":19411,"output":421,"cacheRead":114176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134008,"cost":{"input":0.0485275,"output":0.006315,"cacheRead":0.028544,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0833865}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776409760069,"responseId":"resp_02ad8e5e7b4217730169e1dca12f0481919de785136a26dbba"}}
