ide check:\n\n```bat\ndocker compose ps\n```\n\nIf you paste that, I can tell you immediately whether the restart actually succeeded or if we need to recover anything.\n\nAlso, after a restart, we’ll likely want to restart the memory daemon again:\n\n```bash\n./scripts/memory_backup_daemon.sh start\n```","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_02ad8e5e7b4217730169e1dde7e398819187005e5c19ca981b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":20365,"output":579,"cacheRead":114176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":135120,"cost":{"input":0.050912500000000006,"output":0.008685,"cacheRead":0.028544,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.08814150000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776410074818,"responseId":"resp_02ad8e5e7b4217730169e1dddb21248191ad73efd57b15329f"}}
