**11.7 MB** total\\n- mostly `.txt` research exports\\n- plus:\\n  - `MyActivity.html`\\n  - one `.pdf`\\n  - one `.xlsx`\\n- there are clear duplicates and near-duplicates\\n- there are clearly multiple project families, at least **Apollo** and **Aurelius**\\n\\nSo the next steps should be practical and staged.\\n\\n**Recommended pipeline, phase 2: robust project ingestion**\\n\\n1. **Inventory and fingerprint the corpus**\\n   - create a machine-readable manifest\\n   - detect exact duplicates\\n   - flag probable near-duplicates by filename/content similarity\\n\\n2. **Project classification**\\n   - bucket files into projects like:\\n     - Apollo\\n     - Aurelius\\n     - Other / Unknown\\n   - include Gemini conversation entries from `MyActivity.html`\\n\\n3. **Conversation reconstruction**\\n   - group related Gemini entries by project\\n   - sort them chronologically\\n   - concatenate into per-project timelines\\n   - keep source-level provenance\\n\\n4. **Operational document generation**\\n   For each project, generate:\\n   - `timeline.md`\\n   - `master_context.md`\\n   - `decisions.md`\\n   - `tasks.md`\\n   - `deliverables.md`\\n\\n5. **Clean ingestion set for LightRAG**\\n   - ingest both:\\n     - source documents\\n     - distilled project docs\\n   - this gives better recall plus better synthesis\\n\\n6. **Then grow into phase 3**\\n   - agent tasking\\n   - monitoring\\n   - UI/workflow orchestration\\n   - project-aware mission prompts\\n\\n**What I would do next, concretely**\\n1. build the **manifest + dedupe report**\\n2. create **project folders** under `vault/Clean/projects/`\\n3. classify the raw docs into **Apollo / Aurelius / Other**\\n4. generate the first two project timelines:\\n   - Apollo\\n   - Aurelius\\n\\nThat gives us the spine of the whole system.\\n\\n**Suggested folder structure**\\n- `vault/Clean/projects/apollo/`\\n- `vault/Clean/projects/aurelius/`\\n- inside each:\\n  - `sources/`\\n  - `timeline.md`\\n  - `master_context.md`\\n  - `decisions.md`\\n  - `tasks.md`\\n  - `deliverables.md`\\n\\n**My recommendation**\\nStart with this exact execution order:\\n1. **manifest + dedupe**\\n2. **project classification**\\n3. **Apollo timeline**\\n4. **Aurelius timeline**\\n5. **summary docs**\\n6. **LightRAG ingestion**\\n\\nIf you want, I can start now by generating:\\n- a corpus manifest\\n- a duplicate report\\n- initial Apollo/Aurelius project buckets\\n\\nThat’s the right next move.\",\"textSignature\":\"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_0beebb82725bec5a0169e096bc07b88191b2916b92e470b65f\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"}],\"api\":\"openai-codex-responses\",\"provider\":\"openai-codex\",\"model\":\"gpt-5.4\",\"usage\":{\"input\":168,\"output\":605,\"cacheRead\":39296,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":40069,\"cost\":{\"input\":0.00042,\"output\":0.009075,\"cacheRead\":0.009824,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0.019319}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1776326329395,\"responseId\":\"resp_0beebb82725bec5a0169e096b9582c8191985b87b9acc3a2e6\"}}\nIntel/agents/main/sessions/95ab2a64-b730-4d1a-b975-fbff48fab4e2.jsonl.reset.2026-04-16T08-08-02.405Z:154:{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"4f5ceb44\",\"parentId\":\"9ee94efa\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-16T08:00:40.512Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"call_5aShV9aYoXSDlkiqSeuuiwRr|fc_0beebb82725bec5a0169e0971e0c6c819199468bf13527af6b\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"python3 - <<'PY'\\nfrom pathlib import Path\\nimport json, re, shutil\\n\\nraw = Path('/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/vault/raw')\\nbase = Path('/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/vault/Clean/projects')\\nprojects = {\\n    'apollo': base / 'apollo' / 'sources',\\n    'aurelius': base / 'aurelius' / 'sources',\\n    'other': base / 'other' / 'sources',\\n}\\nfor p in projects.values():\\n    p.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\\n\\nrules = [\\n    ('aurelius', [r'\\\\baurelius\\\\b', r'\\\\bhfmp\\\\b', r'post-finasteride', r'post-androgen', r'androgen', r'pelvic floor', r'photobiomodulation', r'neuroendocrine', r'metabolic', r'erectile', r'bh4', r'pterin', r'proviron', r'mesterolone', r'pfs', r'pssd']),\\n    ('apollo', [r'\\\\bapollo\\\\b', r'project apollo', r'openclaw', r'lightrag', r'crawl4ai', r'gemini conversations', r'vault', r'architectur', r'knowledge engine', r'mcp', r'ollama', r'open webui']),\\n]\\n\\nmanifest=[]\\nfor f in sorted(raw.iterdir()):\\n    if not f.is_file():\\n        continue\\n    name = f.name.lower()\\n    project = 'other'\\n    for label, pats in rules:\\n        if any(re.search(p, name) for p in pats):\\n            project = label\\n            break\\n    dest = projects[project] / f.name\\n    if not dest.exists():\\n        shutil.copy2(f, dest)\\n    manifest.append({'file': f.name, 'project': project, 'copied_to': str(dest)})\\n\\n(base / 'classification.json').write_text(json.dumps(manifest, indent=2), encoding='utf-8')\\n\\nfor proj in ['apollo','aurelius','other']:\\n    count = sum(1 for x in manifest if x['project']==proj)\\n    print(proj, count)\\nprint(base / 'classification.json')\\nPY\",\"workdir\":\"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace\",\"yieldMs\":10000,\"timeout\":120},\"partialJson\":\"{\\\"command\\\":\\\"python3 - <<'PY'\\\\nfrom pathlib import Path\\\\nimport json, re, shutil\\\\n\\\\nraw = Path('/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/vault/raw')\\\\nbase = Path('/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/vault/Clean/projects')\\\\nprojects = {\\\\n    'apollo': base / 'apollo' / 'sources',\\\\n    'aurelius': base / 'aurelius' / 'sources',\\\\n    'other': base / 'other' / 'sources',\\\\n}\\\\nfor p in projects.values():\\\\n    p.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\\\\n\\\\nrules = [\\\\n    ('aurelius', [r'\\\\\\\\baurelius\\\\\\\\b', r'\\\\\\\\bhfmp\\\\\\\\b', r'post-finasteride', r'post-androgen', r'androgen', r'pelvic floor', r'photobiomodulation', r'neuroendocrine', r'metabolic', r'erectile', r'bh4', r'pterin', r'proviron', r'mesterolone', r'pfs', 